VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT PreparedStatement(\s)*(\.|->)execute( |Query|Update)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(\+|String\.format|MessageFormat|append\() && MISSING:setString\(|setInt\(|setLong\(|setObject\()
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential SQL injection vulnerabilities in Java code that uses prepared statements.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Input(s) in SQL Query (PreparedStatement).
